profile:
Twilight Wall Beds makes upright and side-tilt wallbeds for both residential and commercial markets.
Twilight Wall Beds is the only wall bed dealer who makes and sells it's products right in Nanaimo. The owner and all employees live locally which keeps your money in the local economy helping to build our community.
